column4: NSLOCTEXT("[578AF142457994B42A1838A018395C2A]", "F390682C4D227BF76AB31F9FF1D1CB9A", "It\'s the Speedy Time Zone beyond this point. Don\'t get too close.")
NSLOCTEXT("[578AF142457994B42A1838A018395C2A]", "2222D8E04470158A1ED2D7A77DA11DE5", "There are two goals for me. One is to find the Island\'s danger.")
NSLOCTEXT("[578AF142457994B42A1838A018395C2A]", "E71FFE844009DB7D936639AAD2BA2497", "The other is to get Digimon into the city.")
NSLOCTEXT("[578AF142457994B42A1838A018395C2A]", "94407B664B79BD3F9200CEA16F6BF9AC", "I can\'t. I gotta guard this forest.")
NSLOCTEXT("[578AF142457994B42A1838A018395C2A]", "5BF9FACC465ACBECB07CD1B96539BF32", "Then, do you know anything about the island\'s danger?")
NSLOCTEXT("[578AF142457994B42A1838A018395C2A]", "1D5A5F4D421A58CF11C368B7BA26E813", "I remember a big rock falling from the sky not too long ago.")
NSLOCTEXT("[578AF142457994B42A1838A018395C2A]", "F38E6AB04EC0CF9A563CC0B22A070292", "In Speedy Time Zone. On the other side of the forest.")
NSLOCTEXT("[578AF142457994B42A1838A018395C2A]", "8E1CBE914B2CA663E4AB61A04D1D0C50", "Let me go! I may be able to find some clues!")
NSLOCTEXT("[578AF142457994B42A1838A018395C2A]", "DB7BCA514DE6CDC3427C12BFE3A768A2", "If you insist. Go ahead and check it out.")
NSLOCTEXT("[578AF142457994B42A1838A018395C2A]", "F5BA545A4A1367C11F7F85A7992E9D5A", "Beyond this point, time goes twice as fast. Take enough food with you.")
NSLOCTEXT("[578AF142457994B42A1838A018395C2A]", "802357594BD80750D28CDEAD9ABDE243", "You must also watch out for growing too old.")
NSLOCTEXT("[578AF142457994B42A1838A018395C2A]", "0FFC70264848E74213B36BBD25CF8AD5", "Looks like a meteorite! It\'s nothing to worry about.")
NSLOCTEXT("[578AF142457994B42A1838A018395C2A]", "E64126B14A60CED6DB38809E678720DB", "But Master, who will guard the Ancient Dino Region?")
NSLOCTEXT("[578AF142457994B42A1838A018395C2A]", "A3E6079949055A1156CEF39D34E1B314", "This is a critical time for the island. Go to the city and help the others!")
NSLOCTEXT("[578AF142457994B42A1838A018395C2A]", "5B605E8A4D94776385444EA577AC633A", "He is still young, but please put him to work. I will stand guard here.")
NSLOCTEXT("[578AF142457994B42A1838A018395C2A]", "02BF113A4A95B12F62B2A09EA490491F", "{Player}, that\'s the story, so can I go to the city?")
